Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃之王…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是統率黃色軍團的Lv.9的超頻連線者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但黃色軍團所支配的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是上野到秋葉原這一帶才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼他們會出現在池袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  都是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你一手策劃的鬧劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow  Radio！
